quran[77]{c,v,t}:
  25,1,"Naab ning yɩ wagelle, sẽn sik-a Welegrã (Gafã) A yambã zugã sẽn na yɩl t'a yɩ dũni wã neb bugsda."
  25,2,"Naab ning sẽn so saas la tẽnga, A pa tar biiga, A pa tar lagem-n-taag A naamẽ wã ye, A naana bũmbã fãa n kɩt t'a zems zemsg tεkẽ."
  25,3,"La b rɩka soab-rãmb zẽms sẽn pa Yẽnda, soab-bãmb pa naan baa fʋɩ, bãmb mensã yaa sẽn naane, b pa tõe n tak nafre maa naong n kõ b mensã ye, b pa so kũum, b pa so vɩɩm, b pa so (ki n tɩ) yikã ye."
  25,4,"La neb nins sẽn kɩflã yeelame: ""ad wãnde pa baa fʋɩ rẽnda zĩri-beedo, tɩ neb a taab sõng-a"". ad bãmbã wa ne wẽgb la zĩrimbeedo."
  25,5,"La b yeele: ""yaa pĩnd rãmb soalem la a kɩt tɩ b gʋlsdẽ, tɩ b togsd-a yibeoog la zaabr t'ɑ kelgdẽ''."
  25,6,"Yeele: ""yaa Naab ning sẽn mi yel-solgdɩ saasẽ wã la tẽngẽ wã n sik-a, A yaa Yaafg Naaba n yaa Yolsg Naaba."
  25,7,"La b yeele: ""yaa bõe n tar Tẽn-tʋʋm kãngã t'a rɩtẽ la a kẽngd raasẽ? B sã n rag n sik malεk n naag-a tɩ yẽ me bugsdẽ."
  25,8,"Maa b kõ-a arzεk baoore, maa a tall pʋʋg n rɩt beenẽ?"" La wẽgdbã yeel yã: ""ad yãmb pa tũud rẽnda rao b sẽn maan tɩɩm''."
  25,9,"Ges b sẽn bilgd foom ne ned ningã! B menemame n ka tõe n yek (sɩdã) sor ye."
  25,10,"Naab ning yɩ wagelle, t'A sã n tʋlla, A kõta foom sõmblem sẽn yɩɩd woto, pʋt tɩ koom zoet b tẽngrã la A kõ foom gɑsdo."
  25,11,"Pa woto ye, ad b yagsa dũni wã yikri, la Tõnd segla Bug-witg n kõ neb nins sẽn yagsd dũni wã yikrã."
  25,12,"Bugmã sã n wa yã bãmb zãrgẽ, b wʋmda a sũ-yikrã la a kudbã."
  25,13,"B sã n wa lob bãmb Bugmã pʋgẽ, zĩ-sẽkẽ n loe-b ne taaba, la b na n kos tɩ (Wẽnd) sãɑm bãmb (tɩ sε)."
  25,14,"Rũnda, ra kos-y sãang a yembr ye, kos-y sãang wʋsgo."
  25,15,"Yeele: ""woto la sõmã bɩ yaa paab arzãnã b sẽn pʋlem wẽn-zoεtbã, ad a yaa bãmb keoor la b lebgr zĩiga."
  25,16,"B tara a pʋgẽ b sẽn tʋlle, b yaa paadba, ad yaa fo Soabã pʋlenga sẽn rog A zugu."
  25,17,"Raar ning b sẽn na n tigim-b la b sẽn tũud bũmb nins zẽng sẽn pa Wẽndã, t'A yeel-ba: ""rẽ yĩnga yaa yãmb n menes Mam yembsã bɩ yaa bãmb n menem sore?"""
  25,18,"La b na n yeele:"" yɩlgemd be ne Foom, pa sõmb ne tõnd tɩ d rɩk zẽng sẽn pa Foom n maan lall-n-taag ye, la ad Fo maana bãmbã la b saam-rãmbã wʋm-noog hal tɩ b wa yĩm Tẽegrã n yɩ bõn-rãmba."
  25,19,"(Rʋbsã) yagsa yãmb y sẽn yeel bũmb ningã, y pa tar põsgr zĩiga, y le pa tar sõngr zĩigã, ned ning sẽn wẽg a meng yãmb sʋka, D na n lembs-a-la sɩbgr sẽn bedme."
  25,20,"La Tõnd pa tʋms Tẽn-tʋʋmb sẽn reng foom taoore, rẽndame tɩ b ra rɩtame la b kẽngd raasẽ, la Tõnd maana yãmb tɩ yaa zarbg ne taaba, sẽn na yɩl n gese y na n maana sugri? La fo Soabã yaa Neta."
  25,21,"La neb nins sẽn pa tẽed Tõnd sεgbã yeel yã: ""b sã n da sika tõnd nengẽ malεgs maa d sã n da tõe n yãndẽ tõnd Soabã""; ad bãmbã waooga b mens la b kedg kedgr sẽn yaa bedre."
  25,22,"Raar ning b sẽn na n yã malεgsã, nin-wẽnsã ka na n paam kɩba-noog ye, [malεgsã] na n yeelame: "" sũ-noogr ne yãmb yaa gɩdgr sẽn ta tεka""!"
  25,23,"Tɩ Tõnd rɩk b sẽn da tʋm (dũni kaanẽ wã) n maan-a t'a lebg tom sẽn sãeege."
  25,24,"Arzãn nebã ra-kãngã n yɩɩd sõmblem neer ne zĩndg-zĩiga, la yɩɩd neer ne vʋʋsem zĩiga."
  25,25,"Lɑ tẽeg raar ning saasã sẽn na n wa pãrg n bɑs sawad-fɑɑse tɩ malεgsã sig sigb tεkẽ."
  25,26,"Sɩda, naamã ra-kãngã raarã yaa Yolsg Naab n so-a, a na n yɩɩ raar sẽn na n yɩ kãenkãe ne kɩfr-rãmbã."
  25,27,"Lɑ tẽeg raar ning wẽgd sẽn na n rũm a nus a yiib n yeele: kɑto! Mam sã n rag n pʋga Tẽn-tʋʋmã pɑ sãoo."
  25,28,"M wɩɩbdo kato! Mam sã n rag n ka gãd a zagl n maan zao!"
  25,29,"Ad a menemsa maam Tẽegrã (Alkʋrãanã) sẽn wa n wa mam nengẽ wã poorẽ, lɑ a sʋɩtãan zoet n basa ninsaalã (a sẽn wat n zarb-a poorẽ)."
  25,30,"La Tẽn-tʋʋmã yeel yã: ""yaa m Soabã! ad mam nebã wãag n basa Alkʋrãanã""."
  25,31,"Lɑ yaa woto la D maan bε n kõ nabiyaam fãa, sẽn yi nin-wẽnsẽ wã, la ad fo Soabã kãndgrã la A sõngrã sekame."
  25,32,"La neb nins sẽn kɩflã yeel yã: ""yaa bõe yĩng la b pa sik Alkʋrãanã a zug vugri""? Tõnd sik-a-la woto sẽn na yɩl n rɩk-a n tabl fo sũurẽ wã, la Tõnd karem-a lame n tũnug taaba."
  25,33,"B pa wat ne bilgr rẽndame tɩ Tõnd waa ne fo nengẽ ne sɩd la welgr sẽn yɩɩd sõma."
  25,34,"Neb nins b sẽn na n tigim n vub-b b ninsã zut n kẽng Gεhannemã, bãmb rãmb zĩig n yɩɩd wẽng la yɩɩd sor menengo"
  25,35,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka, Tõnd kõo a Musa Gafã la D maan a ma-biigã n lɑgm-ɑ tɩ yɑɑ sõngda."
  25,36,"Rẽ poorẽ, Tõnd yeelame: ""kẽng-y-yã, yãmb y yiibã fãa, neb nins sẽn yags Mam Aaya-rãmbã nengẽ"". Rẽ poorẽ tɩ Tõnd halk-b halkr tεka."
  25,37,"La a Nuuh nebã b sẽn wa n yags Tẽn-tʋʋmbã, Tõnd bõr-b lame la D maan-b tɩ b yaa tagmas ne Tõnd tõogã n kõ nebã, la D segl sɩbgr sẽn zabd wẽgdbã yĩnga."
  25,38,"La a ʿAad la a Ṯamuud rãmba, la Rass nebã (kʋɩlgẽ rãmbã) la zãma wʋsg sẽn zĩnd bãmbã wakatã sʋka."
  25,39,"Ãnkam fãa Tõnd sifɑ reng-tɑoor rãmbɑ sãɑngã n wing-bɑ, la ãnkam fãa Tõnd halkame halkr tẽkẽ."
  25,40,"Lɑ bãmb pɩʋʋga tẽng ningã zu-beed saagã sẽn ni wã, rẽ yĩnga b pa yã-a-la, bãmbã pʋs n pa tẽed tɩ (b sã n ki) b na n yik-b lame ye."
  25,41,"B sã n wa yã foom la b sẽn sãbsd foom (n yetẽ): ""rẽ yĩnga yaa yã wã la Wẽnd sẽn tʋms tɩ yaa Tẽn-tʋʋmã bɩ?"""
  25,42,"Kella bilf t'a menes tõnd n yi d soab-rãmbã tũudum sã n ka tõnd sẽn maan sugr b zugu!"" Yɩ bilfu b na bãnge, b sã n wa yãnd naongã, ãnd n yɩɩd ne sor menengo''."
  25,43,"Rẽ yĩnga fo yãnda ned ning sẽn rɩk a yamleoog tɩ yaa a zu-soaba, yaa foom n na n yɩ a yel-bobendã?"
  25,44,"Maa fo tẽedame tɩ b sẽn waoog fãa wʋmdame bɩ b tagsdame? Ad b yaa wala rũmsi, b menengã pʋs n yɩɩda rũmsi."
  25,45,"Fo pa yãnd fo Soabã sẽn yεdg maasmã to-to, A sã n ratɑ, A rag n na maan-a t'a yãs zĩig a yembre, lɑ Tõnd maanɑ wĩntoogã t'a yaa tɑgms n wĩngd mɑɑsmã, t'ɑ woglemã lɑ ɑ goεεlmã tũngdɑ wĩntoogã."
  25,46,"Rẽ poorẽ tɩ Tõnd mobg-a n kẽng Tõnd nengẽ mobgr sẽn yaa yol-yole."
  25,47,"Yaa Yẽnda la sẽn maan yʋngã n kõ yãmbã tɩ yaa fuugu, la gõeemã tɩ yaa vʋʋsgo, la wĩndgã tɩ yaa lebg-n-kẽng tʋʋma."
  25,48,"Yaa Yẽ la Naab ning sẽn tʋms sebgã tɩ yaa sũ-noogr sẽn lʋt A yolsgã taoore, la Tõnd sigsa saasẽ wã sa-ko-yɩlgemde."
  25,49,"Sẽn na yɩl n vʋʋg tẽng sẽn da kʋɩ n pelg la D yũnug rũms la ninsaalb wʋsg Tõnd sẽn naane."
  25,50,"Ad Tõnd pʋɩya tɑgmes-rãmbã Alkʋrãɑnɑ pʋgẽ bãmb sʋka sẽn na yɩl tɩ b tẽege, la b wʋsg fãa tõdgame n maan sõm-zɩɩlem."
  25,51,"La tɩ Tõnd sã n ra tʋllame, D rag n na tʋms Bugsda tẽng fãa nengẽ."
  25,52,"Bɩ f ra wa tũ kɩfr-rãmbã ye, la tall Alkʋrãanã n maan-b tak-n-taar sẽn yaa bedre."
  25,53,"Lɑ yaa Yẽnda la Naab ning sẽn kegl mog a yiibã, wãnde yaa ko-noog n yaa maasga, tɩ wãnde yaa yamsem n yaa toog liga, la A ning b yiibã sʋka gɩdr sẽn pa pasgde."
  25,54,"La yaa Yẽnda la sẽn naan ninsaal n yi koomẽ, n maan-a t'a tar buud la reemdo, la fo Soabã yaa tõogd ne bũmb fãa."
  25,55,"La b tũud zẽng sẽn pa Wẽnde, bũmb sẽn pa nafd-ba la pa namsd-ba, lɑ ad kɩfr ra yɩɩme n yaa lall-n-taag ne a Soabã bεεba."
  25,56,"La Tõnd pa tʋms foom rẽndam tɩ f yɑɑ sũ-noogd la bugsda."
  25,57,"Yeele: ""mam pa kot yãmb keoor a zug ye, rẽnda ned ning sẽn wa n rata n gãd kãndgr sor n tʋg a Soabã nengẽ."
  25,58,"La bobl f meng ne Vɩt ning sẽn pa kiidã la yɩlg a Yʋʋrã, ad A minimã ne A yembsã zunuubã sekame."
  25,59,"Yaa Yẽnd la Naab ning sẽn naan saasã la tẽngã la bũmb ning sẽn be b sʋkã rasem a yoobe pʋgẽ, rẽ loogr poorẽ tɩ Yolsg Naab zẽke Al-ʿaršã (Naamã goeel) yĩngri (zẽkr sẽn tog ne Wẽnde), Yẽ lɑ yolsg-nɑɑbã bɩ f sok-A ned ning sẽn tar-a kɩbar n yɩɩda."
  25,60,"Lɑ b sã n yeel-ba: ""maan-y Yolsg Naabã suguudu"", la b sẽn yetde: ""yaa bõe la Yolsg Naaba?"" tɩ rẽ paasd-b zoe-n-zãage."
  25,61,"Naab ning sẽn ning-a ãdsã saasẽ wã yɩ wagelle, la A maan fɩtl (wĩntoogo) beenẽ la kiuug sẽn vẽene."
  25,62,"Yaa yẽnda la Naab ning sẽn naan-a yʋngã la wĩndgã tɩ b ledsd taaba, ne ned ning sẽn rat-a n tẽege maa sẽn rat-a n soeese Wẽnde."
  25,63,"Lɑ Wẽnd yembsã la neb nins sẽn kẽnd tẽn-gãngã zug ne bʋg-bʋge la zɩtbã sã n wa gom ne-b la b sẽn yetde: ""tɩlgr"" gomde."
  25,64,"Bãmb rãmbã la neb nins sẽn tat yʋng n maan b Soabã suguud la b yãs A taoor (n kotẽ),"
  25,65,"Bãmb la neb nins sẽn yete: ""yaa tõnd Soaba! zãag tõnd ne Gεhannem Bugmã"", ad a naongã yaa sẽn duumdi."
  25,66,"Ad a tablg zĩig la a zĩndg zĩig yɩ wẽnga."
  25,67,"Bãmb la neb ninsi, tɩ b sã n na n yãk (arzεk) n nafe, b pa maan tɩ zʋʋge, b pa maan bõn-zoeer me, b yãnesda tẽng-n-sʋka."
  25,68,"Bãmb la neb nins sẽn pa boond soab zẽng n lagem Wẽnde, la b pa kʋʋd yõor ning Wẽnd sẽn gɩdgã rẽndame tɩ tũu ne hakε, b leb n pa yood ye, la ned ning sẽn tʋm woto, a na n paama sɩbgre."
  25,69,"B na n fão wã naongã n kõ-a Yikr raarã la a na n duuma beenẽ ne faagre;"
  25,70,"Rẽnda ned ning sẽn tuub-a la a kõ sɩda la a tʋm sõma, bãmb rãmbã Wẽnd teemda b yel-wẽnsã tɩ lebg yel-sõma, la Wẽnd yɩɩme n yaa Yaafg Naab n yaa Yolsg Naaba."
  25,71,"La ned ning sẽn tuubi la a maan tʋʋm sõma, ad a tuubgã pata Wẽnd nengẽ."
  25,72,"Leb n yaa bãmb la neb nins sẽn pa maand kaset zĩri la b sã n na n pɩʋʋg gom-yaar zĩigẽ, b pɩʋʋgd zãn-zãnd n zãag-b mensã ne-bɑ."
  25,73,"La bãmb la neb nins tɩ b sã n na n karem b Soabã Aaya-rãmb b nengẽ, b pa maand b mensã mugs la zoens ye."
  25,74,"La bãmb la neb nins sẽn yete: ""yaa tõnd Soaba! kõ tõndo, sẽn yi tõnd pagbẽ wã la d koambẽ wã nif-mɑɑre, la maan tõnd tɩ d yɩ wẽn-zoetbã taoor-rãmba."
  25,75,"B na n yaoo bãmb-rãmbã (arzãn) roogo, b sẽn maan sugrã yĩnga, b na n seg-b lame ne pʋʋsg la tɩlgre."
  25,76,"B na n duuma beenẽ, ad tablg zĩig la zĩndg zĩig yɩ neere."
  25,77,"Yeele: ""mam Soabã toog ka be ne yãmb sã n ka yãmb kosgã yĩnga, ad yãmb yagsame, la ket bilfu sɩbgrã na n yɩɩ tɩlae ne yãmba."
